title: Plat 5 AKA Wood 10 looking for a team!
body: Hello friends, so yeah I'm not looking for anything in specific, can be a serious team trying to go places or a team just messing around, I don't mind what solo queue rank everyone is, honestly I'm mainly just wanting to get some ranked 5's end of season rewards :D I'm happy to play any role, with mid / jg / adc being my most played, probably jungle.
